headline: Duke Energy supports local conservation efforts with $550,000 in funding for North Carolina environmental impact programs
summary: Duke Energy today announced $550,000 in grants for environmental impact programs in North Carolina. The funding will support a variety of projects aimed at enhancing and preserving the state's natural surroundings.
